Here are projects that I developed with others. You may find them useful if you work on machine learning, or more generally, computer science.
Zero-shot KG Reasoning
Zero-shot reasoning on any knowledge graph.
Scalable KG Reasoning
Path-based reasoning for million-scale knowledge graphs.
Multi-hop Reasoning
Neural-symbolic model for multi-hop logical queries on knowledge graphs, with strong performance and interpretability.
Inductive KG Reasoning
Knowledge graph reasoning framework inspired by traditional path-based methods.
Platform for Drug Discovery
Powerful and flexible machine learning platform for drug discovery.
Graph Embedding System
General and high-performance graph embedding system, with support of various applications and popular models.
Paper List for Graphs
Comprehensive list of recent deep learning literature for graphs.
Mahjong AI
Development toolkit for Chinese official Mahjong, with efficient search algorithms and interface for machine learning.
Dynamic Dictionary Matching
Efficient parallel implementation of hash-based dynamic dictionary matching.
